      "text": "（はぁ、はぁ……苦しい……）\n（こんなステージ、初めて……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Huff‚ huff… This is hard…)\n(I've never been on a stage like this before…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.1343333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 8.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "（まだ、たったの二曲目なのに）\n（こんなに消耗してるなんて……どうして？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(It's only our second song‚)\n(but I'm already this exhausted… Why?)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
