    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "（……楽しい……！！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(…This is fun…!!)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 30.9
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 30.9
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 40.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "みんな……苦しそう……でも、凄く楽しそう\nあんなサニーピース、見たことない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone… They look in pain… But they also look so happy.\nI've never seen Sunny Peace like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……多分、あの一曲で、全部出し切ってしまったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…They probably gave it their all in that one song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 47.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "そんな……！　一曲だけで？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No way…! In just one song?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "今のサニピは超集中状態に入ってる\nその代償に、スタミナを激しく消耗しているんだろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sunny Peace is in a state of hyperfocus.\nIn exchange‚ their stamina is being severely depleted.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 57.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "確かにそれだけ凄いステージでした\nなのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It certainly was an amazing stage.\nAnd yet…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ああ……さらにその上をいっている",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… They're going even further.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 66.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "……怖いくらいです\n観ていると、心が持っていかれそうな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It's scary.\nIt feels like my heart is being pulled in…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "さくらと……サニーピースと\nまるで一つになったみたいな感覚",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With Sakura… with Sunny Peace‚\nit's like we've become one.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 81.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（麻奈……観てるか？　さくらは……サニーピースは）\n（お前の、その先に行ったよ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Mana… Are you watching? Sakura… Sunny Peace)\n(has gone beyond you.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 90.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（きっと琴乃達も、そこに行ける）\n（だから麻奈、見守っていてくれ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I'm sure Kotono and the others can reach that level too.)\n(So‚ Mana‚ watch over them.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.6,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4733.33333330001,
          "startTime": 99.3333333333
        }
