    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 99.1
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 99.1
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_sun-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 99.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 107.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "はぁっ……はぁっ……みんな、ありがとう……\nこれ、が……私達の、全てです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huff… Huff… Thank you‚ everyone…\nThis… is… everything we have!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 112.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ……こ、こんなに苦しくて、でも楽しいの\n初めてです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe… Th-this is so hard‚ but it's the most fun\nI've ever had…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 119.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "このまま……死んでもいいかも\n……って、少しだけ……思った",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wouldn't mind… dying like this.\n…I thought that‚ for a little bit…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 126.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それなら年齢的には、私が一番最初かも……あはは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-well‚ then I guess I'd be the first one to go‚ considering my age… Ahaha.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "……十七歳なんでしょ？　大丈夫大丈夫……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You're seventeen‚ aren't you? It's okay‚ it's okay…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 134.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 138.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "みんな……。サニーピースと、みんなが\n今日、一つになれました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone… Sunny Peace and everyone here\nbecame one today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 146.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_14_02-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "きっとこのステージは\n私達だけじゃ、作れなかった空間",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sure this stage\nis a space we couldn't have created alone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 156.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
